<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Withdraw Funds</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      The Withdraw Funds page lets creators securely transfer earned revenue to their bank account
      or preferred payment method. This page ensures timely and secure payouts while keeping
      full records of all transactions.
    </p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-4">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Sections Included:</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Available Balance:</strong> Shows the funds available for withdrawal.</li>
          <li><strong>Withdrawal Form:</strong> Select amount, payment method, and input account details.</li>
          <li><strong>Withdrawal History:</strong> Track past transactions, their status, and dates.</li>
          <li><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Displays estimated time for payment to reach your account.</li>
          <li><strong>Security & Verification:</strong> Optional two-factor authentication or email confirmation for safety.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">User Process on Withdraw Funds Page:</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Login and navigate to Withdraw Funds page.</li>
          <li>Check Available Balance to know how much can be withdrawn.</li>
          <li>Enter withdrawal amount and choose preferred payment method.</li>
          <li>Provide bank or payment account details as required.</li>
          <li>Submit the withdrawal request.</li>
          <li>Monitor Withdrawal History for status updates (pending, completed, rejected).</li>
          <li>Wait for processing time, then confirm funds receipt in your account.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-4 mb-2">Purpose of This Page:</h2>
